title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1984-07-13
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Dire Wolf, CC Rider, Loser, Cassidy, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Hell In A Bucket-> Might As Well

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Touch Of Gray-> Fire On The Mountain-> Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Dark Star*

* Dark Star for the planetary alignment

reviews.review_text: 5 Star Sugar Mag! One Of The Best Sugar Mags Ever.

Still awesome after 28 years. (Cassette was given me in '93 by my philosophy prof in uni)
     Gloriously cathartic jam in "Scarlet Begonias" – the true spirit of the band emerges as an astonishing triumph of beauty. Jaw-dropping crescendo – doubled over when the boys catch up with Jerry.
     "Sugar Magnolias" is great and "Stella Blue" is poignant and powerful. Other good stuff too!
